# 🌍 Scenario 5 — Impossible Travel Alert

## 🎯 Alert
> “Sign‑ins from UK and Brazil within 2 minutes.”

## 🔍 Investigation
- Check IP reputation  
- Check MFA prompts  
- Review audit logs  
- Confirm user location  

## 🛑 Containment
1. Reset password  
2. Revoke sessions  
3. Block suspicious IP  

## 🔧 Remediation
- Enforce MFA if not enabled  
- Review Conditional Access  
- Monitor for further attempts  

## 📝 Ticket Note
Impossible travel alert triggered. User confirmed they were not in Brazil. Reset password, revoked sessions, and blocked IP. No further suspicious activity detected.

