# 🧪 Scenario 7 — Device Non‑Compliant (Security Risk)

## 🎯 User Report
> “I can’t access Teams — it says my device is not compliant.”

## 🔍 Investigation
- Check Intune compliance  
- Check OS version  
- Check encryption status  
- Check antivirus status  

## 🛑 Containment
- Block access until compliant  
- Enforce Conditional Access  

## 🔧 Remediation
- Update OS  
- Enable BitLocker  
- Update Defender  
- Re‑sync device  

## 📝 Ticket Note
Device non‑compliant due to missing OS updates and disabled BitLocker. Guided user through updates and encryption. Device became compliant and access restored.

