# 🔥 Scenario 8 — Ransomware Behaviour Detected

## 🎯 Alert
> “Mass file encryption behaviour detected.”

## 🔍 Investigation
- Check Defender alert chain  
- Identify patient zero  
- Review file activity  
- Check lateral movement  

## 🛑 Containment
1. Immediately isolate device  
2. Disable user account  
3. Block malicious process  
4. Notify security team  

## 🔧 Remediation
- Restore files from backup  
- Patch vulnerabilities  
- Review admin permissions  
- Conduct post‑incident review  

## 📝 Ticket Note
Ransomware behaviour detected. Device isolated and account disabled. No lateral movement observed. Files restored from backup. Escalated to security team for full incident review.

